      "cooked": "<p>Hi, sorry I am not understanding exactly.  In my mind slope mode and resistance mode are the same just different unit of measurement but I am not sure if that is actually true and especially not sure for a specific trainer.  What happens when you use slope mode and shift to set power targets?</p>\n<p>Here I show how I design shorter efforts in slope mode<br>\n<a href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/t/example-of-a-hiit-4-second-interval-automated-slope-mode-workout/\">https://forums.trainerday.com/t/example-of-a-hiit-4-second-interval-automated-slope-mode-workout/</a></p>",
